          "reviewBody": "It's Ramkrishna Vivekananda Mission CBSE Board based school at Agarpara, Tetultala. I have been told that it's under Kesto Maharaj of Ramakrishna Vivekananda Mission, Barrackpore. I just liked the school during my first visit. There is great environment is always encouragble for students. Everything is there what students need these days. So big areas, trees and big playground. It's a great treat for yours eyes, mind and heart when you see the students playing and enjoying themselves. Regarding study culture, it's too good. A perfect blend of our Bengali culture with CBSE Board's norms and guidelines. They have their own website and you can visit to get more informations.",
